THE LAWNMOWER MAN · node LMM · LMM · The Lawnmower Man · New Line Cinema · 1992 — dir. Brett Leonard

universe of origin : a suburb and a virtual-reality lab in the early-90s VR fever — gyroscope rigs, polygon cyberspace, and the dream of jacking in
